    "body": "Use ES6 class for `RemixTests`\r\n\r\n```\r\n// index.js\r\nclass RemixTests {\r\n    constructor (verbosity) {\r\n        const logger = new Log(verbosity)\r\n    }\r\n    ....\r\n}\r\nmodule.exports = RemixTests\r\n```\r\n\r\n```\r\n// remix-ide\r\nimport { RemixTests } from 'remix-tests'\r\nconst remixTests = new RemixTests()\r\n```\r\n\r\n```\r\n// run.js\r\nimport { RemixTests } from 'index.js'\r\nconst RemixTests = new RemixTests(verbosity)\r\n```\r\n`verbosity` is a number param `1,2` or `3` representing `[error, warning, debug]`",
